      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of sophisticated engineering and proven reliability. This meticulously maintained vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver, offering a premium experience at a compelling value. Having passed our comprehensive multi-point safety and performance inspection, it stands ready for the road with a clean history and a well-preserved aesthetic. From its responsive handling to its refined interior, every detail confirms its history of responsible ownership. This is a turnkey investment in quality, providing the confidence and prestige you expect from a top-tier dealership.",
      "price": 36800.0,
