    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute pride and joy. She\u2019s been a dream to drive and has been looked after like one of the family. You might find a tiny bit of character here and there from our weekend adventures, but she\u2019s reliable, smooth, and still has that spark that makes every drive special. I\u2019ve kept her well-maintained and she\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more memories. Come by and take her for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love just like I did!",
      "price": 34500.0,
