    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted performance icon, engineered for the driver who values mechanical sympathy and peak volumetric efficiency. This chassis remains incredibly taut with zero subframe deflection, and the high-revving powerplant pulls with linear urgency across the entire powerband. I\u2019ve recently performed a comprehensive refresh of the cooling system, including a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak during spirited sessions. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp short-throw shifter and a lightened flywheel that significantly reduces rotational inertia for lightning-fast rev-matching. Suspension geometry has been optimized with adjustable toe links and refreshed bushings to ensure surgical turn-in bite. This isn't just a car; it's a precision instrument with all major preventative maintenance\u2014including VANOS seals and rod bearing inspection\u2014fully addressed. Recent fluid analysis confirms the internal health of the block is stellar.",
      "price": 38500.0,
